      <span class="bold">A quick summary of the functions of the kidney:</span> 
      <ul>
        <li>
          Acts as a filter system 
        </li>
        <li>
          Gets rid of waste products 
        </li>
        <li>
          Balances the body's fluid content 
        </li>
        <li>
          Produces <a href="glossary.php#Hormone">hormones</a> that control <a href="glossary.php#Blood_pressure">blood pressure</a> 
        </li>
        <li>
          Produces the hormone <a href="glossary.php#Erythropoietin">Erythropoietin</a> to help make red <a href="glossary.php#Blood_cells">blood cells</a> 
        </li>
        <li>
          Activates vitamin D to maintain healthy bones
        </li>
      </ul>
